Investment Strategies    





Investment Strategies :: Redwood Investments LLC
Redwood Investments focuses on sectors in which it has demonstrated expertise: media, real estate, and alternative energy.  The firm will make debt or equity investments in profitable entities with a minimum $5 million annual revenue. The firm will also invest in professionally managed private equity or venture funds specializing in these fields. The desired size of investments is $1-5MM per transaction. Maximum investment size is $10MM.
Examples of investments recently made or under review:
Media

digital media
proprietary  data
trade shows, conferences and events

Real Estate

